devdoc.details: Store and manage user agreements on data usage purposes

addAgreement(bytes32,uint256,bool).details: Record a new agreement in the contract

params._consent: The user's consent (true for agree, false for disagree)
params._purposeBlockHash: The hash of the purpose block related to the agreement

getAgreementsLength().details: Returns the number of agreements stored in the contract
